rent%20to%20Emoff's%20two%20children%20from%20a%20previous%20marriage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhat%20he%20said%20was%20abhorrent.%20It%20was%20stupid%2C%20uninformed%2C%20and%20I%20think%20the%20reaction%20of%20not%20only%20the%20country%20but%20the%20world%20%E2%80%94%20I%20mean%2C%20look%20at%20what%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cbsnews.com%2Fnews%2Fjennifer-aniston-jd-vance-childless-cat-ladies%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJennifer%20Aniston%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20%E2%80%94%20it%20has%20touched%20a%20chord%20in%20a%20way%20that%20has%20just%20upset%20nearly%20everyone%2C%20because%20everyone's%20family%20is%20their%20family%20%26quot%3B%20Emhoff%20told%20former%20US%20Attorney%20Preet%20Bharara%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpodcasts.apple.com%2Fus%2Fpodcast%2Fthe-second-gentleman-on-kamalas-campaign-with-doug-emhoff%2Fid1265845136%3Fi%3D1000663466223%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBharara's%20podcast%20%3C%2Fa%3Ein%20an%20episode%20published%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmhoff%20said%20that%20Vance's%20remarks%20show%20he%20doesn't%20appreciate%20the%20reality%20of%20a%20modern%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20you're%20telling%20many%20people%20in%20this%20country%20and%20this%20world%20that%20they%20don't%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20Emhoff%20said.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20the%20only%20thing%20that%20matters%20is%20this%20so-called%2C%20you%20know%2C%20old%20fashioned%20view%20of%2C%20you%20know%2C%20traditional%20quote%20unquote%20family%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3B%3Cspan%3EAnd%20it%20is%20so%20abhorrent%20and%20I%20am%20so%20proud%20of%20Kirsten%2C%20who%20we%20love%20so%20much%20and%20we%20are%20so%20close%20and%20we%20have%20coparented%2C%20the%20three%20of%20us%2C%20so%20brilliantly%20and%20seamlessly%20and%20it%20hurt.%20It%20hurt%20my%20feelings.%20It%20was%20upsetting%20and%20I%20was%20so%20proud%20of%20our%20daughter%2C%20Ella%2C%20who%20supported%20her%20mother%20and%20her%20mothers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmhoff's%20daughter%2C%20Ella%20Emhoff%2C%20and%20his%20ex-wife%2C%20Kerstin%20Emhoff%2C%20had%20already%20teed%20off%20on%20Vance%20over%20previously%20coming%20after%20their%20family.%20Both%20Ella%20and%20her%20brother%20Cole%20were%20teenagers%20when%20Emhoff%20and%20Harris%20were%20married.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThese%20are%20baseless%20attacks.%20For%20over%2010%20years%2C%20since%20Cole%20and%20Ella%20were%20teenagers%2C%20Kamala%20has%20been%20a%20co-parent%20with%20Doug%20and%20I%2C%26quot%3B%20Kerstin%20Emhoff%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20CNN.%20%26quot%3BShe%20is%20loving%2C%20nurturing%2C%20fiercely%20protective%2C%20and%20always%20present.%20I%20love%20our%20blended%20family%20and%20am%20grateful%20to%20have%20her%20in%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVance's%20comments%20have%20only%20exacerbated%20his%20struggle%20to%20introduce%20himself%20to%20the%20nation.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjd-vance-lowest-vice-president-approval-rating-republican-convention-2024-7%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHe's%20already%20set%20a%20record%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20being%20the%20most%20disliked%20major%20vice%20presidential%20nominee%2C%20even%20after%20a%20party%20convention.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaylor%20Van%20Kirk%2C%20a%20spokesperson%20for%20Vance%2C%20said%20that%20the%20senator's%20old%20remarks%20were%20being%20mischaracterized.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnce%20again%2C%20the%20leftwing%20media%20have%20twisted%20Senator%20Vance's%20words%20and%20spun%20up%20a%20false%20narrative%20about%20his%20position%20on%20the%20issues.%20The%20Democrats%20are%20in%20complete%20disarray%20with%20the%20most%20unpopular%20Vice%20President%20in%20history%20as%20their%20party's%20nominee%2C%26quot%3B%20Van%20Kirk%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20Business%20Insider.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202021%20interview%2C%20Vance%2C%20who%20went%20on%20to%20get%20elected%20to%20the%20US%20Senate%2C%20was