2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20said%2C%20assembly%20couldn't%20be%20easier%3A%20you%20attach%20the%20stake%20to%20the%20center%20pole%2C%20tap%20the%20combined%20poles%20into%20the%20sand%20until%20you%20reach%20the%20pole's%20red%20line%20(if%20you%20go%20past%20the%20line%2C%20the%20corner%20columns%20could%20slack)%2C%20place%20the%20canopy%20onto%20the%20center%20pole%20(it%20helps%20to%20have%20someone%20assist%20when%20it's%20windy%20out)%2C%20extend%20the%20four%20metal%20arms%20(begin%20with%20the%20arm%20on%20the%20windiest%20side%2C%20then%20move%20to%20the%20opposite%20arm%2C%20repeating%20with%20the%20two%20remaining%20arms)%2C%20all%20the%20while%20filling%20each%20fabric%20pocket%20with%20sand%20after%20each%20arm%20extension.%20And%20that's%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20makes%20it%20stand%20out%5C%22%3EWhat%20makes%20it%20stand%20out%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20safety%20factor%20is%20the%20main%20reason%20I%20love%20this%20cabana.%20A%20few%20years%20ago%2C%20I%20wrote%20a%20story%20for%20HGTV%20Magazine%20about%20the%20dangers%20of%20not%20properly%20securing%20a%20beach%20umbrella%20in%20the%20sand%2C%20which%20can%20act%20like%20a%20missile%20in%20the%20wind%2C%20resulting%20in%20serious%20injuries%20and%20even%20death.%20For%20all%20the%20summers%20I've%20spent%20at%20the%20shore%2C%20I've%20never%20felt%20completely%20comfortable%20with%20a%20unipole%20umbrella%2C%20no%20matter%20how%20well%20I'd%20secure%20it%20in%20the%20sand.%20Whenever%20the%20wind%20would%20pick%20up%2C%20I'd%20close%20the%20umbrella%20down%2C%20leaving%20my%20family%20without%20sun%20protection.%20Thanks%20to%20its%20unique%20pole%20design%20and%20four%20sandbagged%20corners%20(which%20hold%20up%20to%2040%20pounds%20of%20sand)%2C%20there's%20little%20risk%20of%20the%20CoolCabana%20releasing%20into%20the%20air.%20Some%20other%20reasons%20I'm%20passionate%20about%20this%20cabana%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EYou%20can%20fit%20multiple%20beach%20chairs%20under%20the%20canopy.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221814%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22four%20beach%20chairs%20placed%20under%20the%20canopy%20of%20the%20coolcabana%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a3cc901a227600e631fc52%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221361%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20cabana%20is%20roomy%20enough%20for%20multiple%20chairs%2C%20plus%20extras%20like%20towels%20and%20a%20cooler.%3Cp%3EColleen%20Sullivan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20typical%20beach%20umbrella%20provides%20a%20canopy%20of%20about%206'%20in%20diameter%20(28%20square%20feet%20of%20shade)%20and%20is%20suitable%20for%20two%20chairs.%20The%20CoolCabana%20comes%20in%20two%20sizes%3A%20the%20medium%20opens%20up%20to%206'7%26quot%3B%20x%206'7%26quot%3B%20(43%20square%20feet%20of%20shade)%20to%20comfortably%20fit%20three%20chairs%2C%20and%20the%20large%20opens%20up%20to%208'%20by%208'%20(64%20square%20feet)%2C%20making%20it%20ideal%20for%20four%20chairs.%20It%20would%20take%20more%20than%20two%20typical-sized%20beach%20umbrellas%20to%20shade%20the%20same%20number%20of%20people%20under%20one%20large%20CoolCabana.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EThe%20canvas%20fabric%20is%20rated%20a%20UPF%2050%2B.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EUPF%20(ultraviolet%20protection%20factor)%20is%20the%20standard%20assessment%20used%20to%20measure%20the%20effectiveness%20of%20sun-protective%20fabrics.%20The%20CoolCabana%20is%20rated%2050%2B%2C%20the%20highest%20number%20possible%2C%20meaning%20its%20reinforced%20fiberglass%20polyester%20fabric%20blocks%2098%25%20of%20the%20sun's%20UVA%20and%20UVB%20rays.%20I%20love%20that%20the%20water-resistant%20fabric%20comes%20in%20multiple%20color%20options%20(from%20tan%20to%20yellow%20to%20blue)%20and%20prints%20(stripes%2C%20florals%2C%20and%20graphic%20patterns).%20I%20opted%20for%20the%20bestselling%20tan%20stripe%2C%20which%20I%20believe%20looks%20the%20most%20stylish%2C%20like%20something%20you'd%20see%20at%20a%20posh%20hotel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EIt%20doesn't%20obstruct%20water%20views%2C%20nor%20is%20it%20noisy.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20some%20coastal%20towns%2C%20officials%20are%20banning%20the%20use%20of%20cabanas%20on%20the%20beach%20because%20they%20block%20the%20view%20of%20the%20ocean%20and%20make%20a%20flapping%20noise%20when%20the%20wind%20blows.%20Like%20a%20traditional%20umbrella%2C%20the%20CoolCabana%20has%20a%20single%20pole%2C%20allowing%20for%20clear%20sight%20lines.%20And%20unlike%20the%20cabanas%20that%20feature%20paraglider%20fabric%2C%20the%20CoolCabana%20doesn't%20snap%20and%20thrash%20in%20the%20wind%20%E2%80%94%20it%20barely%20makes%20a%20peep.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EIt%20comes%20with%20a%20sturdy%20carrying%20case.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221726%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20woman%20in%20a%20bathing%20suit%20on%20the%20beach%2C%20carrying%20a%20coolcabana%20across%20her%20shoulder%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a3ccd11a227600e631fcc3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221294%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20CoolCabana%20is%20lightweight%20and%20easy%20to%20carry.%20Its%20duffle%20keeps%20my%20hands%20free%20to%20carry%20other%20items%20like%20beach%20chairs%20and%20towels.%3Cp%3EColleen%20Sullivan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDermatologists%20note%20if%20sunscreen%20isn't%20user-friendly%2C%20people%20won't%20use%20it.%20The%20same%20could%20be%20said%20for%20a%20beach%20umbrella%20%E2%80%94%20if%20it's%20cumbersome%20to%20transport%2C%20you%20may%20just%20leave%20it%20at%20home.%20Unlike%20clunky%20beach%20umbrellas%20that%20often%20come%20with%20plastic%20storage%20sleeves%20that%20rip%20after%20a%20few%20unpackings%2C%20the%20CoolCabana%20features%20a%20sturdy%20canvas%20bag%20equipped%20with%20two%20handles%20%E2%80%94%20the%20shoulder%20strap%20frees%20up%20your%20hands%20so%20you%20can%20carry%20towels%20and%20other%20beach%20accessories.%20The%20medium%20and%20large%20sizes%20are%20both%20reasonable%20weights%2C%20at%2013%20and%2014%20pounds%20respectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EIt%20works%20on%20grass%2C%20too.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EI%20can't%20count%20the%20number%20of%20hours%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20sat%20on%20the%20sidelines%20at%20our%20kids'%20soccer%2C%20baseball%2C%20and%20lacrosse%20summer%20tournaments%20only%20to%20end%20up%20with%20sunburns%20after%20spending%20multiple%20hours%20under%20the%20blistering%20July%20and%20August%20sun.%20The%20CoolCabana%20can%20be%20used%20on%20grass%20%E2%80%94%20the%20company%20offers%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-72026-20%26h%3D30cab6789cd9d0f363e6442b14e467980123979c2305e6a6c0d147bae531c3bd%26postID%3D66a3a40ed290cb433ad52beb%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fcool-cabana-review%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fgo.skimresources.com%252F%253Fid%253D35871X943606%2526url%253Dhttps%25253A%25252F%25252Fcoolcabanas.com%25252Fproducts%25252Fgrass-kit%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekit%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20includes%20a%20hammer%20and%20spikes%20to%20hold%20the%20canopy%20in%20place.%20You%20can%20also%20use%20the%20cabana%20on%20a%20hard%20surface%20by%20placing%20the%20pole%20in%20an%20umbrella%20stand%20and%20water%20bottles%20in%20each%20of%20the%20four%20sand%20pockets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EIt's%20easy%20to%20clean.%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221999%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22a%20woman%20unpacking%20a%20coolcabana%20from%20its%20carrying%20case%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66a3cd4baab37011780adf1d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20the%20day%2C%20all%20the%20CoolCabana%20parts%20pack%20up%20easily%20into%20its%20carrying%20duffle.%3Cp%3EColleen%20Sullivan%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CoolCabana%20is%20low