oman's%20Decision%3A%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20woman's%20decision%20whether%20to%20continue%20the%20pregnancy%20or%20go%20ahead%20with%20medical%20termination%2C%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20observed%20while%20hearing%20a%2015-year-old%20rape%20victim's%20plea%20for%20abortion%20at%2032%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20also%20said%20even%20if%20she%20decides%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20pregnancy%20and%20put%20the%20child%20up%20for%20adoption%2C%20the%20duty%20lies%20on%20the%20State%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20is%20carried%20out%20as%20privately%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllowing%20the%20continuation%20of%20pregnancy%20after%20counselling%20of%20the%20victim%20and%20her%20parents%20of%20the%20risks%20involved%20with%20medical%20termination%20at%2032%20weeks%20pregnancy%2C%20a%20bench%20comprising%20justices%20Shekhar%20B%20Saraf%20and%20Manjive%20Shukla%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThis%20court%20is%20also%20of%20the%20opinion%20that%20a%20woman's%20decision%20in%20whether%20or%20not%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20termination%20of%20her%20pregnancy%20is%20a%20decision%20that%20is%20to%20be%20taken%20by%20no%20one%20but%20herself.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20primarily%20based%20on%20the%20widely%20acknowledged%20idea%20of%20bodily%20autonomy.%20Here%2C%20her%20consent%20reigns%20supreme%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%20while%20hearing%20the%20girl's%20petition%20filed%20through%20her%20lawyer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEven%20if%20she%20decides%20to%20go%20ahead%20with%20the%20pregnancy%20and%20put%20the%20child%20up%20for%20adoption%2C%20the%20duty%20lies%20on%20the%20State%20to%20ensure%20that%20it%20is%20carried%20out%20as%20privately%20as%20possible%20and%20also%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20child%2C%20being%20a%20citizen%20of%20this%20land%2C%20is%20not%20stripped%20of%20the%20fundamental%20rights%20that%20are%20enshrined%20in%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20bench%20said%20in%20its%20order%20dated%20July%2024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThereby%2C%20it%20is%20the%20State's%20duty%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20adoption%20process%2C%20too%2C%20is%20carried%20out%20in%20an%20efficient%20manner%20and%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bbest%20interests%20of%20the%20child%26quot%3B%20are%20followed%2C%20the%20bench%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20girl%2C%20aged%2015%20years%20according%20to%20her%20high%20school%20marksheet%2C%20was%20living%20in%20the%20house%20of%20her%20maternal%20uncle.%20In%20his%20complaint%2C%20he%20claimed%20that%20she%20was%20%26quot%3Benticed%26quot%3B%20away%20by%20a%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBased%20on%20the%20complaint%2C%20an%20FIR%20under%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20section%20363%20(punishment%20for%20kidnapping).%20Upon%20recovery%20of%20the%20girl%2C%20the%20charge%20of%20rape%20and%20provisions%20of%20the%20POCSO%20Act%20were%20added.%20Subsequently%2C%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20the%20petitioner%20was%2029%20weeks%20pregnant.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20noted%20that%20since%20the%20petitioner%20is%2015%20years%20old%2C%20the%20offence%20of%20statutory%20rape%20had%20been%20committed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20was%20examined%20by%20three%20separate%20teams%20of%20doctors%20and%20the%20chief%20medical%20officer%20in%20his%20report%20stated%20that%20though%20the%20continuation%20of%20pregnancy%20would%20impact%20the%20physical%20and%20mental%20well-being%20of%20the%20victim%2C%20medical%20termination%20of%20pregnancy%20at%20this%20stage%20was%20not%20possible%20without%20any%20threat%20to%20the%20life%20of%20the%20victim.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20a%20pointed%20query%20by%20the%20court%2C%20it%20was%20stated%20that%20despite%20the%20risks%20involved%2C%20the%20parents%20of%20the%20victim%20were%20consenting%20to%20termination%20of%20pregnancy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EConsidering%20various%20judgments%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20where%20medical%20termination%20was%20not%20allowed%20at%20later%20stages%20of%20pregnancy%2C%20the%20high%20court%20counselled%20the%20petitioner%20and%20her%20parents%20regarding%20the%20risks%20involved%20with%20the%20termination%20of%20pregnancy%20at%2032%20weeks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEventually%2C%20the%20petitioner%20and%20her%20parents%20agreed%20to%20continue%20with%20the%20pregnancy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722016980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fmpbrq8a_allahabad-high-court_625x300_19_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwhether-to-continue-pregnancy-or-not-is-a-womans-decision-allahabad-high-court-6196825%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It%20is%20a%20woman's%20decision%20whether%20to%20continue%20the%20pregnancy%20or%20go%20ahead%20with%20medical%20termination%2C%20the%20Allahabad%20High%20Court%20observed%20while%20hearing%20a%2015-year-old%20rape%20victim's%20plea%20for%20abortion%20at%2032%20weeks.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Lady%20Gaga%20and%20Zinedine%20Zidane%20star%20in%20Olympics%20opening%20ceremony%20as%20thousands%20brave%20rain%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722016860000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F07%2F1920x1080%2Fskynews-lady-gaga-olympics_6640199.jpg%3F20240726180751%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fparis-2024-olympics-opening-ceremony-gets-under-way-with-starring-roles-for-lady-gaga-and-zinedine-zidane-13185552%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lady%20Gaga%20sang%20in%20French%20and%20played%20the%20piano%20as%20she%20performed%20at%20the%20Olympics%20opening%20ceremony%20on%20the%20banks%20of%20the%20River%20Seine%20-%20before%20a%20grand%20finale%20by%20fellow%20singer%20Celine%