0584_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BShould%20I%20Send%20Them%20To%20Lahore%3F%26quot%3B%3A%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20On%20Protesting%20Farmers%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPunjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20on%20Friday%20attacked%20the%20Centre%2C%20asking%20if%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20will%20not%20allow%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20camping%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20and%20Khanauri%20border%20to%20enter%20Delhi%2C%20should%20he%20%26quot%3Bsend%20them%20to%20Lahore%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFarmers%20from%20Punjab%2C%20led%20by%20Samyukta%20Kisan%20Morcha%20(Non-Political)%20and%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Morcha%20(KMM)%2C%20began%20the%20'Delhi%20Chalo'%20march%20on%20February%2013%20to%20press%20the%20government%20to%20accept%20their%20demands%20which%20include%20that%20the%20Centre%20should%20give%20a%20legal%20guarantee%20for%20minimum%20support%20price%20(MSP)%20for%20crops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20were%20stopped%20by%20the%20Haryana%20Police%2C%20which%20had%20set%20up%20barricades%2C%20including%20cemented%20blocks%2C%20on%20the%20Ambala-New%20Delhi%20national%20highway.%20The%20farmers%20have%20been%20camping%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20and%20Khanauri%20border%20points%20since%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20Khanauri%20and%20Shambhu%2C%20the%20border%20has%20been%20fortified%20with%20iron%20nails%20and%20barricading%20so%20that%20farmers%20cannot%20enter%20Delhi.%20The%20government%20runs%20from%20Delhi%20so%20they%20will%20go%20there.%20If%20they%20will%20not%20go%20to%20Delhi%2C%20should%20I%20send%20them%20to%20Lahore%3F%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mann%20said%2C%20while%20addressing%20a%20public%20meeting%20in%20poll-bound%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20chief%20minister%20addressed%20two%20rallies%20--%20one%20in%20Hisar's%20Barwala%20and%20the%20other%20in%20Sirsa's%20Dabwali.%20Haryana%20goes%20to%20polls%20later%20this%20year%20and%20the%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20(AAP)%20has%20said%20it%20will%20contest%20on%20all%20the%2090%20seats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20Barwala%20event%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20said%20even%20four%20years%20ago%2C%20the%20farmers%20were%20stopped%20from%20entering%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20many%20as%20726%20farmers%20died%20during%20the%20farmers'%20protest%20against%20the%20now%20repealed%20farm%20laws%20when%20they%20were%20stopped%20earlier%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mann%20alleged%20that%20people%20of%20Haryana%20gave%20chance%20to%20different%20parties%20but%20they%20all%20looted%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20a%20doctor%20is%20not%20able%20to%20cure%20an%20ailment%20then%20the%20doctor%20should%20be%20changed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20AAP%20leader%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20like%20Delhi%20and%20Punjab%20voters%2C%20people%20of%20Haryana%20should%20also%20%26quot%3Bvote%20for%20'badlav'%20(change)%20this%20time%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mann%20touched%20upon%20several%20initiatives%20of%20the%20AAP%20governments%20in%20Punjab%20and%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Punjab%2C%2043%2C000%20government%20jobs%20have%20been%20given%20purely%20on%20merit%20basis%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20have%20been%20paper%20leak%20incidents%20in%20Haryana%20but%20in%20Punjab%2C%20you%20will%20not%20hear%20such%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mann%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20Punjab%20and%20Haryana%20are%20brothers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20may%20have%20become%20separate%20states%20but%20our%20hearts%20are%20one%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mann%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20are%20giving%20600%20units%20of%20free%20electricity%20to%20everyone%20per%20billing%20cycle%20of%20two%20months%20in%20Punjab%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Mann%20said%20the%20AAP%20government%20in%20Delhi%20has%20reformed%20the%20government%20schools.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BChildren%20of%20poor%20families%20are%20cracking%20top%20competitive%20exams%20in%20Delhi%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20taken%20the%20government%20to%20people's%20doorsteps%20to%20facilitate%20them%20and%20make%20their%20lives%20better%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mann%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20urged%20the%20people%20of%20Haryana%20not%20to%20be%20carried%20away%20by%20the%20promises%20being%20made%20by%20the%20BJP%20and%20the%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarlier%2C%20they%20(BJP%20and%20Congress)%20used%20to%20rule%20by%20turns%20and%20people%20had%20no%20other%20option%2C%20but%20now%20they%20have%20an%20alternative%20in%20the%20AAP%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mann%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20BJP%20has%20been%20in%20power%20for%2010%20years.%20Did%20they%20give%20you%20any%20job%20or%20did%20they%20undertake%20development%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20asked%2C%20while%20addressing%20the%20gathering.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20told%20if%20it%20rains%20for%20one%20minute%20in%20Barwala%2C%20people%20have%20to%20take%20out%20boats.%20Such%20is%20the%20situation%2C%26quot%3B%20Mann%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAttacking%20the%20BJP%20government%20at%20the%20Centre%2C%20he%20said%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20talked%20of%20%26quot%3B400%20paar%26quot%3B%20but%20now%20they%20are%20running%20their%20government%20with%20the%20support%20of%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDelhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20belongs%20to%20Haryana%20and%20he%20changed%20the%20direction%20of%20the%20country's%20politics.%20He%20had%20said%20the%20BJP%20will%20change%20the%20Constitution%20if%20they%20get%20overwhelming%20majority.%20Thankfully%2C%20they%20did%20not%20get%20majority%2C%20otherwise%20they%20would%20have%20changed%20the%20Constitution%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mann%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20at%20Dabwali%2C%20Mr%20Mann%20told%20the%20gathering%20that%20with%20nearly%20three%20months%20to%20go%20for%20the%20Haryana%20polls%2C%20the%20BJP%20will%20give%20%26quot%3Blollipops%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20gave%20this%20lollipop%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20also%2C%20when%20they%20claimed%20to%20have%20reduced%20cooking%20gas%20cylinder%20price%20after%20hiking%20it%20manifold.%20Be%20wary%20of%20their%20lollipops%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Mann%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurther%20taking%20a%20dig%20at%20the%20BJP%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThey%20keeping%20about%20double-engine%20(government).%20Then%20they%20changed%20one%20engine%20midway%20replacing%20(Manohar%20Lal)%20Khattar.%20Was%20the%20engine%20defective%20or%20what%20happened%3F%20Now%2C%20they%20brought%20another%20engine.%26quot%3B%20He%20told%20the%20people%20of%20Haryana%20that%20the%20country%20does%20not%20need%20double%20engine%20but%20it%20needs%20a%20new%20engine.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOnly%20one%20engine%20is%20sufficient.%20Otherwise%20you%20may%20have%20five%20engines%20but%20what%20will%20they%20do%20if%20they%20are%20not%20good%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Mann.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20talked%20about%20several%20initiatives%20of%20his%20government%20in%20Punjab%20taken%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20various%20sections.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722016800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Ftpsqbfrg_bhagwant-mann_625x300_26_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fshould-i-send-protesting-farmers-to-lahore-if-they-not-allowed-to-enter-delhi-asks-mann-6196719%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20on%20Friday%20attacked%20the%20Centre%2C%20asking%20if%20the%20BJP-led%20government%20will%20not%20allow%20the%20protesting%20farmers%20camping%20at%20the%20Shambhu%20and%20Khanauri%20border