20Tamil%20Nadu's%20MK%20Stalin.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStating%20that%20she%20had%20cancelled%2C%20but%20reconsidered%20on%20the%20advice%20of%20senior%20Trinamool%20Congress%20leader%20Abhishek%20Banerjee%2C%20who%20is%20also%20her%20nephew%2C%20the%20Bengal%20chief%20minister%20said%20the%20Union%20Budget%20had%20been%20brazenly%20politicised.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%26quot%3BThey%20say%20the%20Budget%20shows%20cooperative%20federalism%2C%20but%20it%20is%20biased%20politicisation.%20The%20Budget%20is%20total%20deprivation%20of%20states.%20You%20can%20give%20some%20special%20package%20to%20your%20friends%20but%20you%20can't%20deprive%20opposition%20states%20completely%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20asserted%2C%20adding%20that%20states%20have%20to%20be%20empowered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCentre%20should%20only%20have%20external%20affairs%2C%20defence%20and%20internal%20security.%20Finance%20(is%20something)%20they%20have%20destroyed%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20claimed.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E'Scrap%20Niti%20Aayog'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20said%20that%2C%20during%20the%20meeting%2C%20she%20would%20raise%20the%20issue%20of%20West%20Bengal%20%26quot%3Bnot%20getting%20anything%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20Budget%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Rs%201.71%20lakh%20crore%20her%20government%20claims%20the%20Centre%20owes%20the%20state.%20She%20also%20said%20it%20was%20time%20the%20Niti%20Aayog%20was%20scrapped%20and%20the%20Planning%20Commission%20was%20brought%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20(Niti%20Aayog)%20has%20no%20financial%20implications...%20The%20Planning%20Commission%20had%20worked%20well%20for%20India%20since%20Independence.%20It%20was%20mooted%20by%20Subhash%20Chandra%20Bose%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnOn%20being%20asked%20if%20she%20was%20part%20of%20the%20opposition%20INDIA%20bloc%2C%20she%20said%20she%20was%20at%20the%20national%20level%20but%20the%20alliance%20was%20not%20needed%20in%20the%20state.%20%26quot%3BTrinamool%20Congress%20is%20enough%20to%20fight%20the%20BJP%20in%20West%20Bengal.%20Nationally%2C%20we%20are%20with%20INDIA%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20she%20said%20the%20Congress%20had%20gained%20in%20states%20where%20regional%20parties%20are%20strong%20and%20credit%20should%20be%20given%20to%20both.%20She%20also%20predicted%20that%2C%20in%20the%20upcoming%20Assembly%20elections%2C%20the%20Uddhav%20Thackeray-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20faction%2C%20which%20is%20an%20INDIA%20ally%2C%20will%20win%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Congress%20will%20emerge%20victorious%20in%20Haryana%20and%20Hemant%20Soren%20of%20the%20Jharkhand%20Mukti%20Morcha%20would%20remain%20the%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister.%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3Cbr%3E%5CnOn%20Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%2C%20who%20is%20in%20prison%20in%20the%20liquor%20policy%20case%2C%20she%20said%20she%20was%20very%20concerned%20about%20him%20and%20others%20%26quot%3Btargeted%26quot%3B%20by%20the%20BJP-ruled%20government%20at%20the%20Centre.%20%26quot%3BOnly%20agencies%20and%20conspiracies%20cannot%20give%20you%20political%20results%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Banerjee%20also%20met%20Mr%20Kejriwal's%20wife%2C%20Sunita%2C%20on%20Friday%20evening.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722012360000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fpmvpcbd_mamata-banerjee_625x300_26_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fmamata-banerjee-rails-against-budget-but-says-will-attend-niti-aayog-meet-6196468%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Deviating%20from%20the%20stand%20taken%20by%20her%20counterparts%20belonging%20to%20other%20parties%20in%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%2C%20West%20Bengal%20Chief%20Minister%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20has%20said%20she%20will%20attend%20the%20Niti%20Aayog%20on%20Saturday%20because%20it%20is%20in%20the%20interest%20of%20her%20state.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%2