2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ESeat-sharing%20talks%20for%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20elections%20due%20later%20this%20year%20are%20yet%20to%20officially%20begin%20in%20the%20ruling%20coalition%2C%20but%20the%20tussle%20for%20constituencies%20has%20already%20started%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%20The%20Assembly%20has%20288%20seats%20and%20when%20the%20demands%20of%20the%20constituents%20are%20taken%20into%20account%2C%20the%20math%20is%20not%20working%20out%20for%20the%20Mahayuti%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20the%20larger%20NDA%20alliance.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sources%20said%20the%20BJP%20is%20looking%20to%20contest%20at%20least%20150%20seats%2C%20the%20Chief%20Minister%20Eknath%20Shinde-led%20Shiv%20Sena%20is%20aiming%20for%20a%20minimum%20of%20100%20while%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20NCP%20wants%20at%20least%2080.%20Add%20even%20the%20minimum%20figures%20together%20and%20the%20number%20is%20at%20least%2040%20constituencies%20over%20the%20total%20number%20in%20the%20Assembly%2C%20setting%20the%20stage%20for%20disagreements%20and%20protracted%20negotiations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGetting%20the%20math%20right%20becomes%20even%20more%20important%20because%20the%20coalition%20is%20still%20smarting%20from%20the%20defeat%20it%20faced%20in%20the%20state%20during%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20when%20it%20managed%20to%20win%20only%2017%20of%20the%20state's%2048%20seats%20against%20the%20opposition%20Maha%20Vikas%20Aghadi's%2030.%20While%20a%20number%20of%20factors%20played%20a%20role%20in%20the%20poor%20showing%2C%20experts%20said%20the%20disagreements%20over%20seat-sharing%20for%20the%20polls%20also%20played%20a%20role.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESources%20said%20Ajit%20Pawar%20met%20Home%20Minister%20Amit%20Shah%20along%20with%20fellow%20Deputy%20Chief%20Minister%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20of%20the%20BJP%20in%20New%20Delhi%20on%20Thursday%20and%20the%20division%20of%20seats%20figured%20in%20the%20discussion.%20They%20said%20Mr%20Pawar%20is%20under%20pressure%20from%20leaders%20in%20his%20party%20to%20not%20settle%20for%20anything%20less%20than%2080-90%20seats%2C%20reasoning%20that%20it%20should%20contest%20in%20all%2054%20constituencies%20that%20the%20undivided%20NCP%20won%20in%20the%202019%20Assembly%20polls%20and%20at%20least%2030%20in%20addition%20to%20that.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20undivided%20NCP%2C%20led%20by%20Sharad%20Pawar%2C%20had%20contested%20over%20120%20seats%20in%20the%202019%20elections%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20the%20Congress.%20Insiders%20in%20the%20ruling%20coalition%20said%20the%20Ajit%20Pawar%20faction%20of%20the%20party%20is%20aware%20that%20it%20is%20on%20a%20sticky%20wicket%20given%20that%20it%20managed%20to%20win%20only%20one%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20against%20the%20eight%20clinched%20by%20the%20Sharad%20Pawar%20group.%20It%20had%20lost%20even%20the%20Baramati%20constituency%20which%20was%20turned%20into%20a%20prestige%20battle%20by%20Ajit%20Pawar%20by%20fielding%20his%20wife%20Sunetra%20against%20his%20cousin%20and%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20daughter%2C%20Supriya%20Sule.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEver%20since%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20results%2C%20which%20were%20declared%20last%20month%2C%20there%20has%20been%20speculation%20that%20members%20of%20Ajit%20Pawar's%20party%20are%20in%20touch%20with%20Sharad%20Pawar's%20faction%20to%20return%20there%20after%20the%20NCP%20split%20in%20July%20last%20year.%20This%20is%20adding%20to%20the%20pressure%20on%20Ajit%20Pawar%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20party%20can%20field%20enough%20candidates%20so%20that%20disgruntlement%2C%20and%20possible%20switches%2C%20can%20be%20kept%20to%20a%20minimum.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20results%2C%20an%20article%20in%20Organiser%2C%20a%20weekly%20known%20to%20be%20close%20to%20the%20Rashtriya%20Swayamsevak%20Sangh%2C%20had%20criticised%20the%20BJP%20for%20contesting%20the%20elections%20in%20an%20alliance%20with%20Mr%20%C2%A0Pawar's%20NCP%20and%20there%20has%20been%20buzz%20about%20rift%20in%20the%20Mahayuti%20ever%20since.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20allies%20have%20dismissed%20any%20such%20talk%2C%20especially%20after%20the%20coalition%20managed%20the%20numbers%20well%20in%20the%20Member%20of%20Legislative%20Council%20(MLC)%20elections%20earlier%20this%20month%2C%20BJP%20leader%20and%20Union%20Minister%20Narayan%20Rane%20seemed%20to%20stir%20the%20pot%20again%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20at%20a%20press%20conference%20how%20many%20seats%20the%20BJP%20would%20contest%20in%20the%20Assembly%20polls%2C%20he%20said%20in%20jest%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20would%20want%20the%20BJP%20to%20field%20candidates%20in%20all%20288%20seats.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722006960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F9ko7rkcg_devendra-fadnavis-eknath-shinde-ajit-pawar-fadanvis-shinde-ajit_625x300_11_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffor-bjp-and-allies-maharashtra-seat-sharing-hits-a-math-barrier-6195693%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Seat-sharing%20talks%20for%20the%20Maharashtra%20Assembly%20elections%20due%20later%20this%20year%20are%20yet%20to%20officially%20begin%20in%20the%20ruling%20coalition%2C%20but%20the%20tussle%20for%20constituencies%20has%20already%20started%2C%20sources%20have%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ffor-bjp-and-allies-maharashtra-seat-sharing-hits-a-math-barrier-6195693%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22On%20CCTV%2C%20Murdered%20Woman's%20Last%20Moments%20In%20Bengaluru%20Hostel%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20macabre%20murder%20of%20a%20woman%20in%20a%20Bengaluru%20paying%20guest%20(PG)%20facility%20on%20Tuesday%20was%20captured%20on%20CCTV.%20The%20man%20seen%20in%20the%20footage%20has%20not%20been%20identified%20yet%2C%20the%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKriti%20Kumari%2C%2024%2C%20from%20Bi