ut%20Affecting%20Growth%26quot%3B%3A%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20To%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20growing%20economy%20to%20meet%20its%20needs%20and%20aspirations%2C%20borrowing%20is%20a%20must%2C%20but%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20finance%20ministry%20under%20her%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20debt%20is%20reduced%20without%20affecting%20growth%2C%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20has%20told%20NDTV.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20with%20NDTV's%20Editor-In-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia%20on%20Friday%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said%20fixing%20a%20number%20for%20the%20eventual%20fiscal%20deficit%20and%20working%20towards%20it%20with%20temporary%20solutions%20every%20year%20can%20be%20one%20way%20of%20going%20about%20things%2C%20but%20it%20is%20not%20the%20right%20way%20from%20a%20macroeconomic%20perspective.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sitharaman%2C%20who%20became%20the%20first%20finance%20minister%20in%20India's%20history%20to%20present%20seven%20Union%20Budgets%20in%20a%20row%20this%20year%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20have%20chosen%20a%20healthy%20option%20for%20getting%20the%20fiscal%20deficit%20closer%20to%20the%20number.%20Instead%20of%20looking%20at%20the%20number%20alone%2C%20it%20is%20also%20about%20the%20way%20you%20decide%20to%20get%20there.%20An%20obvious%20method%20for%20every%20country%20is%20to%20reduce%20debt%2C%20but%20borrowing%20is%20a%20must%20for%20a%20growing%20economy.%20The%20question%20is%20how%20much%20are%20you%20borrowing%20and%20where%20it%20is%20being%20used.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAre%20you%20using%20it%20for%20asset%20creation%20or%20to%20service%20or%20reduce%20the%20existing%20debt%3F%20If%20the%20growth%20in%20the%20debt%20is%20to%20be%20reduced%2C%20borrowing%20more%20to%20do%20this%20is%20not%20the%20right%20thing.%20So%20you%20borrow%20and%20create%20assets.%20We%20have%20studied%20the%20NK%20Singh%20Committee%20report%20(on%20fiscal%20responsibility)%2C%20held%20discussions%20and%20decided%20that%20we%20won't%20look%20at%20the%20number%20alone%20but%20choose%20the%20right%20path%20to%20reduce%20debt%20without%20affecting%20your%20growth%2C%20desires%20and%20aspirations%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20other%20aspects%20of%20the%20Budget%2C%20the%20finance%20minister%20also%20said%20that%20its%20communication%20has%20become%20much%20simpler%20and%20the%20document%20now%20speaks%20for%20itself%20without%20needing%20an%20intermediary%20or%20expert%20to%20explain%20it.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEach%20budget%20is%20a%20challenge%20for%20its%20contents%20but%20equally%20it%20is%20a%20challenge%20to%20craft%20the%20language%20of%20the%20budget.%20It%20has%20been%20a%20desire%20of%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20that%20the%20budget%20should%20be%20simple%2C%20you%20convey%20it%20simply%20and%20the%20language%20should%20be%20simple%20so%20that%20anyone%20can%20understand%20what%20you%20are%20saying.%20The%20other%20feature%20he%20has%20been%20clear%20about%20from%20the%20beginning%20is%20that%20the%20budget%20should%20say%20everything%2C%20without%20hiding%20anything%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said.%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20try%20to%20fine-tune%20it%20each%20time%20so%20that%20ultimately%20it%20should%20be%20a%20simple%20document.%20In%20my%20childhood%2C%20I%20remember%20the%20budget%20document%20was%20so%20complex%2C%20people%20would%20study%20and%20analyse%20it%20and%20simplify%20it...%20From%20those%20days%20to%2C%20I%20think%2C%20today%20the%20budget%20speaks%20for%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20on%20one%20of%20the%20key%20criticisms%20of%20the%20Budget%2C%20with%20the%20opposition%20claiming%20that%20many%20states%20have%20been%20ignored%20while%20Andra%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar%20-%20ruled%20by%20BJP%20allies%20crucial%20in%20getting%20the%20NDA%20to%20a%20majority%20-%20have%20been%20in%20focus%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said%20that%20has%20not%20been%20the%20case.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStates%20are%20receiving%20allocations%20as%20they%20have%20in%20the%20past...%20no%20state%20has%20been%20denied%20anything.%20The%20Act%20(Andhra%20Pradesh%20Reorganisation%20Act)%20requires%20the%20centre%20to%20support%20(the%20state)%20in%20building%20its%20capital%20city%20and%20developing%20backward%20regions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722003240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fe96318jg_nirmala-_625x300_26_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdebt-must-be-reduced-without-affecting-growth-nirmala-sitharaman-on-fiscal-deficit-6194881%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20a%20growing%20economy%20to%20meet%20its%20needs%20and%20aspirations%2C%20borrowing%20is%20a%20must%2C%20but%20the%20focus%20of%20the%20finance%20ministry%20under%20her%20is%20to%20ensure%20that%20debt%20is%20reduced%20without%20affecting%20growth%2C%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20has%20told%20NDTV.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdebt-must-be-reduced-without-affecting-growth-nirmala-sitharaman-on-fiscal-deficit-6194881%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdebt-must-be-reduced-without-affecting-growth-nirmala-sitharaman-on-fiscal-deficit-6194881%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdebt-must-be-reduced-without-affecting-growth-nirmala-sitharaman-on-fiscal-deficit-6194881%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22LatentView%20Analytics%20reports%20Q1%20net%20profit%20of%20Rs%2038.92%20cr%2C%20revenue%20up%2021%25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722003162000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-07%2F19%2Fthumb%2Ffeaturecrop%2F400X400%2F1721399234-6789.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A