%20initiative%20to%20train%20his%20daughters%20Geeta%2C%20Babita%2C%20Ritu%2C%20Sangeeta%2C%20along%20with%20his%20nieces%2C%20Vinesh%20and%20Priyanka%2C%20faced%20resistance%20from%20villagers%2C%20including%20his%20own%20family.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20life%20inspired%20the%20Aamir%20Khan-starrer%20Bollywood%20movie%2C%20Dangal.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAllowing%20the%20girls%20to%20enter%20the%20mud%20pit%2C%20traditionally%20seen%20as%20a%20male%20domain%2C%20was%20met%20with%20significant%20opposition%20in%20his%20village%20Balali%20in%20Charkhi%20Dadri%20district%20(then%20in%20Bhiwani).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilarly%2C%20almost%20a%20year-and-a-half%20later%2C%20an%20initiative%20to%20allow%20girls%20to%20train%20alongside%20boys%20at%20Chotu%20Ram%20Stadium%20Wrestling%20Centre%20in%20Rohtak%20faced%20societal%20hurdles.%20Former%20wrestlers%2C%20and%20even%20some%20coaches%2C%20expressed%20reservations%2C%20questioning%20%E2%80%9Chow%20goats%20could%20stay%20among%20the%20lions%E2%80%9D%2C%20fearing%20that%20the%20presence%20of%20girls%20would%20distract%20boys%2C%20leading%20to%20indiscipline.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFast%20forward%20to%202024.%20What%20was%20once%20met%20with%20sarcasm%E2%80%94people%20comparing%20girls%20to%20goats%20and%20boys%20to%20lions%2C%20emphasising%20the%20perceived%20disparity%20in%20strength%20and%20prowess%20in%20the%20wrestling%20arena%E2%80%94has%20now%20become%20a%20point%20of%20pride.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaryana%E2%80%99s%20women%20wrestlers%20have%20emerged%20as%20the%20flag%20bearers%20of%20Indian%20wrestling%20on%20the%20global%20stage.%20At%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2Fvideo%2Ffarmers-daughter-set-to-rock-paris-olympics-archery-shorts-parisolympics2024-sports%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2024%20Paris%20Olympics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20India%20is%20represented%20by%20six%20wrestlers%2C%20five%20of%20whom%20are%20women%20from%20Haryana%E2%80%99s%20rural%20landscape%2C%20where%20they%20once%20faced%20stiff%20opposition%20to%20entering%20the%20male-dominated%20sport.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMeet%20the%20team%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20wrestling%20contingent%20in%20Paris%20comprises%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20(50kg)%20from%20Charkhi%20Dadri%2C%20Antim%20Panghal%20(53kg)%20from%20Hisar%2C%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F263525%2Fanshu-malik-first-indian-woman-world-wrestling-championship-winner%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20Anshu%20Malik%20(57kg)%20from%20Jind%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Nisha%20Dahiya%20(68kg)%20from%20Panipat%2C%20Reetika%20Hooda%20(76kg)%20from%20Rohtak%2C%20along%20with%20the%20lone%20male%20wrestler%2C%20Aman%20Sehrawat%20(57kg)%20from%20Jhajjar.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COlympics%20is%20every%20sportsperson%E2%80%99s%20dream%2C%20and%20I%20am%20feeling%20happy%20to%20be%20a%20part%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20biggest%20sporting%20event%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Reetika%20Hooda%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20Kharkara%20Village%20in%20Rohtak.%20%E2%80%9CMoreover%2C%20Indian%20women%20wrestlers%20leading%20the%20Indian%20charge%20in%20Paris%20is%20a%20great%20motivation%20for%20its%20future%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWomen%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20was%20introduced%20in%20the%20Olympics%20at%20the%202004%20Athens%20Games%2C%20and%20Indian%20women%20wrestlers%20made%20their%20debut%20at%20the%202012%20London%20Olympics.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20Phogat%20family%20has%20been%20represented%20in%20every%20Olympic%20Games%2C%20including%20in%20Paris%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20started%20with%20Mahavir%E2%80%99s%20eldest%20daughter%20Geeta%2C%20who%20became%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20first%20woman%20wrestler%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20Olympics%20at%20the%202012%20London%20Games.%20In%20the%20next%20edition%2C%20it%20was%20Babita%20and%20Vinesh%2C%20and%20followed%20just%20by%20Vinesh%20in%20the%202020%20Tokyo%20Olympics.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202024%20Paris%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F170013%2Fwrestling-phogat-dangal-laureus-award-sports%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EVinesh%20will%20be%20competing%20in%20her%20third%20Olympics%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20becoming%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20wrestler%20to%20feature%20in%20three%20quadrennial%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20introduced%20the%20family%20girls%20into%20wrestling%2C%20my%20aim%20was%20an%20Olympic%20medal.%20The%20girls%20have%20won%20all%20the%20medals%2C%20and%20now%20only%20the%20Olympic%20medal%20is%20missing.%20I%20hope%20Vinesh%20will%20win%20it%20this%20time%20in%20Paris%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mahavir%20Phogat%2C%20their%20mentor.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20961px)%20100vw%2C%20961px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240725-WA0590-1722002469.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22961%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Phogat%20sisters.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240725-WA0590-1722002469.jpg%20961w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240725-WA0590-1722002469-225x300.jpg%20225w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240725-WA0590-1722002469-500x666.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240725-WA0590-1722002469-768x1023.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240725-WA0590-1722002469-640x853.jpg%20640w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240725-WA0590-1722002469-150x200.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358785%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Phogat%20sisters.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202010%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20hosted%20in%20New%20Delhi%2C%20saw%20women%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20making%20its%20debut%20in%20the%20Commonwealth%20Games%2C%20and%20the%20performance%20of%20the%20Indian%20women%20wrestlers%E2%80%94three%20gold%2C%20two%20silver%2C%20and%20a%20bronze%E2%80%94changed%20society%E2%80%99s%20mindset%20towards%20women%20wrestlers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPeople%20no%20longer%20recognize%20them%20as%20goats%20but%20have%20started%20seeing%20them%20as%20lionesses%20in%20the%20wrestling%20arena.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%E2%80%99s%20been%20a%20long%20journey%2C%20from%20villagers%20being%20up%20in%20arms%20against%20the%20move%20of%20making%20the%20girls%20slug%20it%20out%20with%20boys%20in%20the%20mud%20pit%2C%20to%20the%20entire%20village%20standing%20in%20their%20honour%20for%20the%20women%20wrestlers%20winning%20medals%20at%20the%202010%20Commonwealth%20Games.%20Since%20then%2C%20Indian%20women%20wrestlers%20have%20excelled%20on%20the%20world%20stage%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Mahavir.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20five%20of%20them%20making%20it%20to%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20speaks%20a%20lot%20about%20women%20wrestling%20in%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202016%20Rio%20Olympics%2C%20an%20edition%20after%20the%20Indian%20women%20wrestlers%20made%20their%20Olympic%20debut%2C%20a%20trainee%20of%20Rohtak%E2%80%99s%20Chotu%20Ram%20Wrestling%20Centre%2C%20Sakshi%20Malik%2C%20became%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20wrestler%20to%20win%20an%20Olympic%20medal.%20She%20won%20bronze%20in%20Rio.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20then%2C%20the%20women%20trainees%20of%20the%20centre%20have%20had%20a%20presence%20in%20every%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202020%20Tokyo%2C%20Seema%20Bisla%2C%20who%20trained%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20at%20the%20centre%2C%20was%20part%20of%20the%20Indian%20wrestling%20contingent.%20Now%2C%20in%202024%20Paris%2C%20the%20centre%20is%20represented%20through%20its%20trainee%20Reetika%20Hooda%2C%20who%20is%20the%20first%20Indian%20woman%20wrestler%20in%20the%20heavyweight%20category%20to%20qualify%20for%20the%20Olympics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CImmediately%20after%20women%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20was%20introduced%20in%20Haryana%2C%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20girls%20began%20making%20their%20presence%20felt%20at%20the%20national%20level%2C%20and%20gradually%20the%20Indian%20women%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20squad%20became%20largely%20an%20all-Haryana%20affair%2C%E2%80%9D%20explains%20Mandeep%2C%20a%20coach%20at%20the%20centre%20under%20whom%20Sakshi%20Malik%20and%20Reetika%20train.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNow%2C%20in%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20the%20women%20wrestlers%20from%20Haryana%20have%20become%20synonymous%20with%20Indian%20wrestling.%20It%20feels%20nice%20that%20you%20have%20contributed%20your%20bit%20to%20this%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20years%2C%20women%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20has%20seen%20a%20vertical%20growth.%20A%20decade%20ago%2C%20there%20were%20around%2020%20girls%20at%20the%20Rohtak%20centre%2C%20and%20now%20the%20number%20has%20crossed%20100.%20And%20I%20am%20only%20talking%20about%20one%20training%20centre.%20Now%20there%20are%20many%20more%20such%20centres%20for%20women%20across%20the%20state%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20coach%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIndian%20women%20wrestlers%20are%20doing%20very%20well%2C%20and%20we%20are%20expecting%20a%20couple%20of%20medals%20from%20them%20in%20Paris%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFamily%20support%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInitially%2C%20when%20society%20was%20not%20accepting%20the%20women%20from%20the%20khap%20land%20of%20Haryana%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20wrestling%20world%2C%20it%20was%20the%20unconditional%20support%20of%20family%2C%20especially%20the%20parents%2C%20that%20kept%20women%E2%80%99s%20wrestling%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMany%20of%20our%20relatives%20are%20from%20a%20sports%20background%2C%20so%20they%20had%20no%20issues%20with%20putting%20the%20family%20girls%20in%20wrestling%2C%20but%20it%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20so%20forthcoming%20from%20the%20ones%20who%20weren%E2%80%99t.%20Whenever%20they%20used%20to%20meet%20us%2C%20their%20main%20concern%20was%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F293092%2Fnikhat-zareen-wins-commonwealth-games-medal-for-india-boxing-world-champion%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewhat%20would%20be%20her%20future%20if%20Reetika%20didn%E2%80%99t%20excel%20in%20wrestling%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20But%20her%20father%20stood%20by%20her%20decision%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20her%20mother%2C%20Neelam%20Devi.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEver%20since%20Reetika%20earned%20the%20Paris%20Olympics%20quota%20place%2C%20the%20same%20relatives%20have%20been%20wishing%20her%20success.%20Hope%20no%20other%20girl%20has%20to%20face%20any%20more%20sarcasm%2C%20especially%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F350331%2Fparvej-khan-haryana-farmer-son-indian-track-athlete-runner-won-gold-sec-championship-usa%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethose%20from%20rural%20areas%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Neelam%20Devi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20684px)%20100vw%2C%20684px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240721-WA0706-1722002484.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22684%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Reetika%20Hooda%20with%20her%20mother%20Neelam%20Devi.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240721-WA0706-1722002484.jpg%20684w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240721-WA0706-1722002484-200x300.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240721-WA0706-1722002484-500x749.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240721-WA0706-1722002484-150x225.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-358786%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EReetika%20Hooda%20with%20her%20mother%20Neelam%20Devi.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20and%20her%20husband%2C%20Jagbir%20Singh%2C%20shifted%20their%20base%20from%20their%20native%20village%20to%20Rohtak%2C%20so%20that%20they%20could%20provide%20better%20education%20to%20their%20kids%20and%20wrestling%20came%20along%20the%20way.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20journey%20of%20Indian%20women%20wrestlers%20has%20not%20been%20easy%20so%20far.%20Apart%20from%20facing%20challenges%20from%20society%2C%20they%20had%20to%20even%20fight%20against%20the%20system%2C%20as%20evidenced%20by%20the%202023%20wrestlers%E2%80%99%20protest%20at%20Jantar%20Mantar%2C%20led%20by%20Sakshi%20Malik%20and%20Vinesh%20Phogat%20among%20others.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20protest%20shocked%20the%20nation%2C%20revealing%20how%20authorities%20deal%20with%20women%20wrestlers%20despite%20their%20laurels%20for%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CGirls%20need%20to%20stop%20feeling%20pity%20for%20themselves%20or%20considering%20themselves%20weak.%20You%20have%20to%20have%20the%20strength%20of%20belief%20in%20yourself.%20The%20first%20step%20has%20to%20be%20taken%20by%20a%20girl%20herself%3B%20everything%20else%20follows%2C%E2%80%9D%20Vinesh%20had%20told%20The%20Hindu.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20time%20has%20changed.%20Now%20Indian%20wrestling%20is%20recognised%20by%20women%20wrestlers%20from%20Haryana.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20has%20been%20written%20by%20Saurabh%20Duggal.%20Edited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722002999000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FIMG-20240725-WA0590-1722002469.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358732%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22With%20gendered%20comparisons%20to%20unsupportive%20relatives%2C%20these%20women%20have%20stood%20strong%20against%20the%20test%20of%20time.%20As%20India%20cheers%20on%20its%20team%20of%20women%20wrestlers%20at%20the%202024%20Paris%20Olympics%2C%20here's%20a%20glimpse%20into%20their%20journey.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Guest%20Contributor%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358732%2Findian-wrestling-team-members-paris-olympics-2024-weight-categories-reetika-hooda-vinesh-phogat-mahavir-phogat-aman-sehrawat%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20Can%20Fuel%20Prices%20Come%20Down%3F%20What%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20Told%20NDTV%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EPetrol%20and%20diesel%20could%20be%20taxed%20under%20GST%20(Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax)%20rather%20than%20VAT%20(Value%20Added%20Tax)%20if%20state%20governments%20agree%20to%20the%20proposal%20and%20fix%20a%20suitable%20rate%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20told%20NDTV%20Profit%20Friday.%20%26quot%3BIf%20they%20fix%20the%20rate%20and%20all%20come%20together...%20and%20decide%20that%20GST%20will%20include%20petroleum%20products%2C%20then%20we%20can%20implement%20it%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuch%20a%20move%20could%20see%20a%20potential%20drop%20in%20prices%20as%20it%20will%20mean%20these%20are%20taxed%20just%20once%20rather%20than%20having%20multiple%20levies%20-%20i.e.%2C%20not%20just%20on%20cost%20of%20production%20but%20also%20the%20centre's%20excise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20present%2C%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20prices%20vary%20from%20state%20to%20state%20because%20each%20has%20a%20different%20tax.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20centre's%20excise%20duty%20is%20levied%20on%20top%20of%20this%2C%20meaning%20the%20end%20consumer%20pays%20tax%20twice%20over%20-%20once%20to%20the%20state%20government%20and%20then%20again%20to%20the%20centre.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoving%20both%20to%20the%20GST%20list%20will%20mean%20there%20is%20one%20uniform%20tax%20applicable%20across%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20could%2C%20in%20theory%2C%20bring%20down%20the%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20petroleum%20products%20are%20taxed%20at%20close%20to%2060%20per%20cent%2C%20with%20the%20state%20gaining%20Rs%202.5%20lakh%20crore%20and%20the%20centre%20making%20Rs%202%20lakh%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20bringing%20petrol%20and%20diesel%20under%20GST%2C%20there%20will%20be%2C%20at%20most%2C%20a%2028%20per%20cent%20tax%20slab%20over%20these%20products%2C%20as%20that%20is%20the%20highest%20slab%20in%20the%20current%20tax%20regime.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20back%20as%20November%202022%20the%20centre%20had%20said%20it%20is%20ready%20for%20this%20move%20but%20left%20it%20to%20the%20states%20to%20decide.%20Union%20Minister%20Hardeep%20Puri%2C%20then%20the%20Petroleum%20Minister%2C%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20the%20states%20make%20the%20move%2C%20we%20are%20ready.%20We%20have%20been%20ready%20all%20along.%20That%20is%20my%20understanding.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20not%20all%20states%20are%20onboard%20with%20this%20idea%20as%20this%20means%20they%20will%20lose%20out%20on%20sizeable%20revenue.%20In%20fact%2C%20in%20December%202021%20the%20GST%20Council%20did%20not%20recommend%20bringing%20petroleum%20products%20under%20its%20umbrella.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722002820000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-05%2Fd3ti52a_windfall-tax_625x300_16_May_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fwill-fuel-prices-come-down-what-nirmala-sitharaman-told-ndtv-6195035%2