0Video%20Shows%20Man%20Driving%20Car%20With%20Daughter%20On%20His%20Lap%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEnsuring%20the%20protection%20of%20children%20and%20keeping%20them%20safe%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20fundamental%20duties%20of%20parents.%20Recently%2C%20a%20video%20went%20viral%20showing%20a%20man%20driving%20a%20car%20with%20his%20young%20daughter%20sitting%20in%20his%20lap.%20The%20video%20has%20sparked%20concern%2C%20with%20many%20users%20slamming%20the%20man%20for%20his%C2%A0%C2%A0%26quot%3Birresponsible%26quot%3B%20act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20clip%20was%20shared%20by%20Dr.%20Ashwin%20Rajenesh%2C%20an%20emergency%20medicine%20expert%20on%20X.%20In%20the%20video%2C%20the%C2%A0young%20child%20is%20seen%20sleeping%20peacefully%20on%20her%20father's%20lap%20while%20he%20is%20driving.%20Later%20she%20is%20seen%20talking%20and%20playing%20with%20her%20father%20as%20he%20drives%20with%20the%20car.%20Dr%C2%A0Rajenesh%20shared%20the%20video%2C%20warning%20other%20parents%20that%20such%20an%20act%20could%20be%20deadly%20for%20both%20the%20child%20and%20her%20father%20in%20case%20of%20an%20accident.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Looks%20adorable.%20But%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20frontal%20collision%20and%20subsequent%20airbag%20deployment%2C%20the%20infant's%20skull%20would%20be%20accelerated%20at%20~320km%2Fhr%206-8%20inches%20into%20the%20man's%20thoracic%20cage%2C%20killing%20both%20instantly.%20Indian%20parents%20need%20a%20harsh%20reality%20check%2C''%20he%20wrote%20while%20sharing%20the%20video.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20wrote%2C%20''I'm%20sure%20that%20this%20dad%20loves%20his%20daughter%20dearly%2C%20and%20I%20really%20wish%20to%20believe%20that%20this%20dangerous%20indulgence%20of%20child%20endangerment%20was%20a%20singular%20lapse%20of%20his%20better%20judgement.%20Hoping%20he%20%26amp%3B%20other%20parents%20can%20realise%20the%20potential%20dangers%20involved%20in%20such%20practices%2C%20and%20do%20better.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20the%20video%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3ELooks%20adorable.%3Cbr%3E%5CnBut%20in%20the%20event%20of%20a%20frontal%20collision%20and%20subsequent%20airbag%20deployment%2C%20the%20infant's%20skull%20would%20be%20accelerated%20at%20~320km%2Fhr%206-8%20inches%20into%20the%20man's%20thoracic%20cage%2C%20killing%20both%20instantly.%3Cbr%3E%5CnIndian%20parents%20need%20a%20harsh%20reality%20check.%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F1KnhIDDwF5%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F1KnhIDDwF5%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Ashwin%20Rajenesh%20MD%20(%40ashwinrajenesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fashwinrajenesh%2Fstatus%2F1816424932705730906%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2025%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeveral%20users%20agreed%20with%20the%20doctor%20and%20highlighted%20the%20risks%20and%20potential%20dangers%20associated%20with%20such%20acts.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20wrote%2C%20''Poor%20judgement%2C%20risk%20assessment%20and%20hazard%20awareness.%20This%20is%20what%20happens%20when%20stupidity%2C%20combines%20with%20ignorance%20of%20road%20safety%20and%20lack%20of%20enforcement%20of%20traffic%20rules.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20commented%2C%20''Also%20the%20irresponsibility%20towards%20other%20drivers%20in%20the%20road%2C%20The%20driver%20of%20this%20car%20is%20constantly%20distracted%20and%20is%20a%20risk%20to%20everyone%20else%20on%20the%20road.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20said%2C%20''They%20need%20to%20be%20careful%20when%20there%20is%20a%20young%20child%20and%20infants%20in%20the%20car.%20One%20wrong%20decision%20and%20mistake%20can%20change%20a%20whole%20life.''%20A%20fourth%20shared%20a%20similar%20incident%20and%20wrote%2C%20''A%20sudden%20brake%20can%20cause%20serious%20damage.%20Once%20in%20my%20teens%2C%20my%20cousin's%20toddler%20was%20sitting%20on%20my%20lap%20in%20the%20front%20seat.%20The%20car%20jumped%20into%20a%20large%20pothole%2C%20and%20I%20heard%20a%20loud%20bang%2C%20which%20I%20thought%20was%20from%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20car.%20It%20was%20the%20sound%20of%20my%20niece's%20head%20banging%20on%20the%20dash.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20details%20of%20where%20and%20when%20the%20video%20was%20filmed%20are%20still%20unknown.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722000960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F34alklrg_man-driving-with-daughter-on-lap_625x300_26_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fso-irresponsible-man-drives-car-with-daughter-on-his-lap-video-sparks-concern-6195019%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Recently%2C%20a%20video%20went%20viral%20showing%20a%20man%20driving%20a%20car%20with%20his%20young%20daughter%20sitting%20in%20his%20lap.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fso-irresponsible-man-drives-car-with-daughter-on-his-lap-video-sparks-concern-6195019%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fso-irresponsible-man-drives-car-with-daughter-on-his-lap-video-sparks-concern-6195019%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fso-irresponsible-man-drives-car-with-daughter-on-his-lap-video-sparks-concern-6195019%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22National%20Testing%20Agency%20Declares%20NEET-UG%20Final%20Results%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20on%20Friday%20announced%20the%20final%20results%20of%20the%20controversy-ridden%20medical%20entrance%20exam%20NEET-UG%2C%20officials%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20results%20were%20declared%20following%20directive%20from%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20after%20taking%20into%20account%20marks%20of%20a%20physics%20question%2C%20which%20the%20NTA%20had%20said%20has%20two%20correct%20answers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20re-revised%20score%20cards%20are%20live%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20senior%20NTA%20official%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EForty-four%20out%20of%20the%2067%20candidates%20who%20were%20earlier%20declared%20toppers%20had%20scored%20full%20marks%20because%20of%20the%20marks%20awarded%20for%20that%20particular%20physics%20question.%20The%20number%20of%20toppers%20was%20later%20reduced%20to%2061%20with%20the%20agency%20withdrawing%20grace%20marks%20awarded%20to%20six%20candidates%20to%20make%20up%20for%20loss%20of%20time%20at%20few%20exam%20centres.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20major%20setback%20to%20unsuccessful%20aspirants%20of%20NEET-UG%202024%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20on%20Tuesday%20dismissed%20the%20pleas%20seeking%20cancellation%20and%20re-test%20of%20the%20controversy-ridden%20exam%2C%20holding%20that%20there%20was%20no%20evidence%20on%20record%20to%20conclude%20that%20it%20was%20%26quot%3Bvitiated%26quot%3B%20on%20account%20of%20%26quot%3Bsystemic%20breach%26quot%3B%20of%20its%20sanctity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20verdict%20came%20as%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20the%20embattled%20NDA%20government%20and%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20(NTA)%2C%20which%20were%20facing%20strong%20criticism%20and%20protests%2C%20on%20streets%20and%20in%20Parliament%2C%20over%20alleged%20large-scale%20malpractices%20like%20question%20paper%20leak%2C%20fraud%20and%20impersonation%20in%20the%20prestigious%20test%20held%20on%20May%205.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20CBI%20is%20probing%20alleged%20irregularities%20in%20NEET-UG%202024%20and%20has%20lodged%20six%20FIRs.%20The%20NEET-UG%20is%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20for%20admissions%20to%20MBBS%2C%20BDS%2C%20AYUSH%20and%20other%20related%20courses%20in%20government%20and%20private%20institutions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(This%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20auto-generated%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722000720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2015-05%2Fexam-results-generic_650x400_41432538129.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fnational-testing-agency-declares-neet-ug-final-results-6195183%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20NEET-UG%20is%20conducted%20by%20the%20National%20Testing%20Agency%20for%20admissions%20to%20MBBS%2C%20BDS%2C%20AYUSH%20and%20other%20related%20courses.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fnational-testing-agency-declares-neet-ug-final-results-6195183%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fnational-testing-agency-declares-neet-ug-final-results-6195183%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Feducation%2Fnational-testing-agency-declares-neet-ug-final-results-6195183%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BNo%20State%20Has%20Been%20Denied%20Anything%26quot%3B%3A%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20Defends%20Budget%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENo%20state%20has%20been%20denied%20anything%20in%20the%202024%20Union%20Budget%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20told%20NDTV%20Friday%20evening%2C%20responding%20to%20opposition%20criticism%20that%20her%20speech%20this%20week%20mentioned%20only%20two%20states%20-%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar%2C%20both%20ruled%20by%20key%20BJP%20allies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sitharaman%2C%20who%20presented%20a%20record-setting%20seventh%20consecutive%20budget%20on%20Tuesday%2C%20said%20the%20centre%20had%20been%20required%20by%20law%20to%20support%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20after%20its%20bifurcation%20in%202014.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BStates%20are%20receiving%20allocations%20as%20they%20have%20in%20the%20past...%20no%20state%20has%20been%20denied%20anything.%20The%20Act%20(Andhra%20Pradesh%20Reorganisation%20Act)%20requires%20the%20centre%20to%20support%20(the%20state)%20in%20building%20its%20capital%20city%20and%20developing%20backward%20regions%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSeveral%20steps%20have%20been%20taken%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years%20(and)%20many%20other%20steps%2C%20as%20per%20the%20Act%2C%20which%20had%20to%20be%20done%20have%20been%20done.%20Yes%2C%20we%20will%20support%20(the%20building%20of%20the%20new%20capital%2C%20Amaravati%2C%20and%20the%20Polavaram%20irrigation%20project)%20...%20Polavaram%20should%20have%20been%20completed%20but%20there%20are%20some%20technical%20issues.%20The%20state%20government%20is%20seized%20of%20the%20matter%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20told%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress-led%20INDIA%20bloc%20had%20criticised%20the%20Modi%203.0%20government%20for%20failing%20to%20provide%20schemes%20or%20even%20mention%20states%20not%20ruled%20by%20the%20BJP%20or%20its%20allies.%20The%20chief%20ministers%20of%20three%20Congress-ruled%20states%20-%20Siddaramaiah%20(Karnataka)%2C%20Revanth%20Reddy%20(Telangana)%2C%20and%20Sukhvinder%20Sukhu%20(Himachal%20Pradesh)%20-%20said%20they%20would%20boycott%20a%20Niti%20Aayog%20meeting%20Saturday%20in%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20meeting%20is%20being%20chaired%20by%20Mr%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EApart%20from%20the%20Congress%2C%20Tamil%20Nadu's%20ruling%20DMK%2C%20also%20an%20INDIA%20bloc%20member%2C%20said%20no%20provision%20has%20been%20made%20for%20infrastructure%20projects%20like%20the%20second%20phase%20of%20the%20Chennai%20Metro%20Rail%20and%20similar%20developments%20in%20Coimbatore.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Wednesday%20Tamil%20Nadu%20Chief%20Minister%20MK%20Stalin%2C%20also%20expected%20to%20boycott%20the%20meeting%2C%20offered%20a%20warning%20to%20Mr%20Modi.%20%26quot%3BThe%20election%20is%20over...%20now%20we%20have%20to%20think%20about%20the%20country.%20Budget%202024%20will%20save%20your%20rule...%20but%20will%20not%20save%20the%20nation.%20Run%20the%20government%20objectively...%20otherwise%20you%20will%20be%20isolated%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Finance%20Minister%20hit%20back%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20telling%20the%20opposition%20no%20budget%20could%20name%20every%20state%20in%20the%20union%20and%20that%20not%20mentioning%20them%20did%20not%20mean%20no%20funds%20would%20be%20given.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EResponding%20particularly%20to%20criticism%20by%20Congress%20boss%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BTo%20the%20point%20he%20raised%20-%20that%20I%20have%20not%20named%20many%20states%20and%20spoke%20only%20about%20two.%20The%20Congress%20was%20in%20power%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20They%20presented%20many%20budgets%20and%20should%20know%20that%20in%20every%20budget%2C%20you%20don't%20get%20an%20opportunity%20to%20name%20every%20state%20of%20this%20country.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMs%20Sitharaman%20also%20said%20the%20budget%20reflected%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20wish%20to%20keep%20things%20simple%2C%20so%20everyone%2C%20and%20not%20just%20subject%20experts%2C%20could%20understand%20India's%20finances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20present%20everything%20upfront.%20There%20is%20no%20fine%20print...%20we%20ensure%20that%20any%20changes%20made%20are%20communicated%20openly%2C%20based%20on%20feedback%20and%20transparent%20processes%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722000300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fmg546qe8_nirmala-sitharaman-ndtv-_625x300_26_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-state-has-been-denied-anything-nirmala-sitharaman-defends-budget-2024-6194796%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22No%20state%20has%20been%20denied%20anything%20in%20the%202024%20Union%20Budget%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20told%20NDTV%20Friday%20evening%2C%20responding%20to%20opposition%20criticism%20that%20her%20speech%20this%20week%20mentioned%20only%20two%20states%20-%20Andhra%20Pradesh%20and%20Bihar%2C%20both%20ruled%20by%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-state-has-been-denied-anything-nirmala-sitharaman-defends-budget-2024-6194796%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-state-has-been-denied-anything-nirmala-sitharaman-defends-budget-2024-6194796%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fno-state-has-been-denied-anything-nirmala-sitharaman-defends-budget-2024-6194796%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Most%20Important%20Ingredient%20In%20Budget%2C%20According%20To%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Union%20Budget%20should%20be%20a%20simple%20document%20that%20everyone%20can%20understand%2C%20Union%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20by%20Editor-in-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGone%20are%20the%20days%20when%20the%20Union%20Budget%20document%20would%20be%20voluminous%20with%20information%20so%20complex%20that%20only%20a%20few%20people%20would%20understand%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Budget%20should%20say%20everything%20it%20has%20to%20say.%20You%20can't%20say%20something%20and%20hide%20something%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20told%20NDTV.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20question%20about%20how%20people%20back%20in%20the%20days%20used%20to%20wait%20for%20the%20%26quot%3Bfine%20print%26quot%3B%20to%20come%20after%20the%20Budget%20speech%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said%20her%20idea%20of%20the%20Union%20Budget%20has%20no%20hidden%20surprises.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDon't%20push%20anything%20under%20the%20carpet.%20That's%20the%20message%20we%20are%20giving.%20It%20(Budget)%20should%20be%20a%20simple%20document.%20When%20I%20was%20young%2C%20I%20remember%20the%20Budget%20document%20was%20thick%20and%20complex%20to%20understand%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEverything%20you%20want%20to%20say%2C%20say%20it%20upfront.%20There%20is%20no%20fine%20print.%20Amendments%20can%20happen%20after%20feedback...%20I%20consult%20everyone%2C%20from%20chartered%20accountants%20to%20businesspeople%20to%20common%20people.%20I%20go%20everywhere%2C%20hearing%20everyone's%20opinion%2C%20and%20then%20come%20back%20to%20make%20the%20Budget%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Finance%20Minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20will%20spend%20Rs%202.66%20lakh%20crore%20on%20rural%20development%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20had%20said%20while%20unveiling%20new%20programmes%20in%20the%20annual%20Budget%20for%20states%20led%20by%20two%20key%20allies%20-%20Bihar's%20ruling%20Janata%20Dal%20(United)%2C%20and%20Andhra%20Pradesh's%20Telugu%20Desam%20Party%20(TDP).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Budget%20spending%20estimate%20of%20Rs%2048.21%20lakh%20crore%20is%201.2%20per%20cent%20higher%20than%20the%20Rs%2047.66%20lakh%20crore%20estimate%20in%20the%20interim%20Budget%20presented%20in%20February%2C%20helped%20by%20a%20bumper%20transfer%20of%20dividends%20from%20the%20Reserve%20Bank%20of%20India%20(RBI)%2C%20while%20the%20fiscal%20deficit%20target%20was%20reduced%20to%204.9%20per%20cent%20of%20the%20Gross%20Domestic%20Product%20(GDP).%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1722000240000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fj7ksq8eg_nirmala098_625x300_23_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fexclusive-the-most-important-ingredient-in-union-budget-according-to-nirmala-sitharaman-6195107%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Union%20Budget%20should%20be%20a%20simple%20document%20that%20everyone%20can%20understand%2C%20Union%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20told%20NDTV%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20by%20Editor-in-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C