0be%20simple%2C%20so%20that%20anyone%20can%20understand.%20It%20should%20be%20in%20simple%20language.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*This%20change%20is%20part%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi's%20vision%20for%20budget%20communication%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*On%20criticism%20that%20the%20budget%20focused%20on%20specific%20states%2C%20the%20finance%20minister%20said%20no%20state%20is%20being%20denied%20its%20due%20support.%C2%A0%26quot%3BStates%20are%20receiving%20allocations%20as%20they%20have%20in%20the%20past.%20No%20state%20is%20being%20left%20behind%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*Regarding%20South%20Indian%20states%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20acknowledged%20their%20developmental%20challenges%20and%20emphasised%20the%20role%20of%20the%20Finance%20Commission%20in%20addressing%20these%20issues.%20They%20should%20seek%20funds%20for%20developmental%20purposes%20based%20on%20their%20achievements%20and%20challenges%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*She%20underscored%20that%20the%202024%20Union%20Budget%20focused%20on%20reducing%20the%20national%20debt%20without%20stifling%20economic%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*Elaborating%20on%20fiscal%20prudence%2C%20she%20said%20that%20borrowing%20is%20not%20a%20great%20way%20to%20reduce%20budget.%C2%A0Debt%20should%20be%20reduced%20without%20affecting%20the%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*The%20goal%20is%20not%20merely%20to%20meet%20deficit%20targets%20but%20to%20manage%20debt%20through%20asset%20creation%20and%20efficient%20borrowing%20practices%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*On%20financial%20regulation%2C%20particularly%20concerning%20derivatives%2C%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20acknowledged%20the%20growing%20interest%20among%20Indians%20in%20these%20investment%20vehicles.%20%26quot%3BWe%20aim%20for%20SEBI%20to%20regulate%20this%20sector%2C%20but%20our%20intent%20was%20to%20indicate%20a%20soft-touch%20regulatory%20approach%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*Speaking%20on%20Foreign%20Direct%20Investments%20from%20China%2C%20the%20finance%20minister%20said%20there%20has%20not%20been%20any%20discussion%20in%20front%20of%20her.%20In%20some%20departments%2C%20there%20have%20been%20talks%20of%20giving%20visa%20to%20some%20sections%2C%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721999100000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2Fmsjh1ka8_nirmala-sitharaman_625x300_26_July_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbudget-should-be-in-simple-language-nirmala-sitharaman-tells-ndtv-highlights-6194720%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Days%20after%20the%20first%20budget%20of%20Modi%203.0%20was%20unveiled%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20speaks%20to%20NDTV's%20Editor-In%20Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fbudget-should-be-in-simple-language-nirmala-sitharaman-tells-ndtv-highlights-6194720%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThis%20Budget%20Offers%20Comprehensive%20Package%20For%20Youth%26quot%3B%3A%20Finance%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ENirmala%20Sitharaman%20presented%20her%20seventh%20consecutive%20Union%20Budget%20earlier%20this%20week%2C%20a%20new%20record.%20Today%2C%20the%20Finance%20Minister%2C%20in%20an%20exclusive%20interview%20to%20NDTV's%20Editor-in-Chief%20Sanjay%20Pugalia%2C%20answers%20the%20questions%20that%20have%20been%20making%20the%20headlines%20since%20the%20budget%20was%20unveiled%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20the%20top%20quotes%20from%20the%20interview%3A%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20This%20budget%20offers%20a%20comprehensive%20package%20for%20youth%20development%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20Our%20intent%20is%20to%20indicate%20a%20soft-touch%20regulatory%20approach%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E*%20To%20reduce%20debt%2C%20burrowing%20is%20not%20a%20great%20way.%20Even%20if%20you%20are%20borrowing%2C%20in