n%20released%20as%20the%20batting%20consultant%20by%20the%20franchise%20ahead%20of%20this%20year's%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2046-year-old%2C%20who%20played%2031%20Tests%20and%202%20ODIs%20for%20India%2C%20was%20the%20batting%20coach%20of%20PBKS%20between%202019-2021%20but%20stepped%20down%20from%20his%20role%20before%20the%20IPL%202022%20auction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPBKS%2C%20who%20have%20not%20made%20it%20to%20the%20playoffs%20since%202014%2C%20blew%20hot%20and%20cold%20during%20the%20entire%20IPL%202024%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20finishing%20ninth%20in%20the%20points%20table.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPBKS%20are%20IPL's%20perennial%20underachievers%2C%20with%20the%20franchise%20one%20of%20the%20four%20teams%20yet%20to%20win%20an%20IPL%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPBKS%20recorded%20the%20highest%20successful%20run-chase%20in%20T20%20cricket%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20chasing%20down%20262%20at%20the%20Eden%20Gardens%20to%20beat%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20by%20five%20wickets.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBayliss%2C%20a%20World%20Cup%20winning%20coach%20who%20also%20guided%20KKR%20to%20two%20IPL%20trophies%2C%20failed%20to%20turn%20an%20inconsistent%20PBKS%20into%20a%20consistent%20outfit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20had%20signed%20a%20two-year%20contract%20with%20the%20Punjab%20side%20back%20in%202022.%20However%2C%20three%20poor%20seasons%20on%20the%20trot%2C%20with%20bottom-half%20finishes%20in%20the%20table%20isn't%20what%202014%20finalists%20were%20looking%20forward%20to.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJaffer%2C%20if%20appointed%2C%20will%20bring%20in%20a%20fresh%20approach%20to%20the%20franchise.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20the%20BCCI%20is%20set%20to%20meet%20with%20all%2010%20teams%20on%20July%2031%20to%20discuss%20the%20number%20of%20retentions%20teams%20can%20make%20and%20the%20Right%20to%20Match%20(RTM)%20options%20in%20hand%20ahead%20of%20IPL%202025%20mega%20auction.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20report%20by%20Cricbuzz%20says%20IPL%20CEO%20Hemang%20Amin%20sent%20text%20me