%20responses%2C%20these%20amenities%20were%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20walking%20path%2C%20play%20area%2C%20open%20air%20gym%2C%20amphitheatre%2C%20basketball%20court%2C%20and%20greenery%20were%20added%20to%20make%20the%20lake%20a%20recreational%20hub%20for%20the%20residents.%20Today%2C%20it%20is%20a%20symbol%20of%20energy%20and%20happiness%20every%20morning%20and%20evening%2C%20as%20hundreds%20of%20people%20gather%20for%20their%20morning%20walks%2C%20children%20play%2C%20and%20everyone%20has%20a%20joyful%20time.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20a%20shining%20beacon%20of%20hope%20for%20what%20can%20be%20achieved%20through%20collective%20efforts.%20Since%20October%202023%2C%20the%20CR%20team%20has%20also%20conducted%20lake%20walk%20tours%20for%20residents%20from%20other%20localities%20who%20wish%20to%20replicate%20this%20model.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20are%20the%20real%20life%20%3Cem%3ENayaks%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20out%20to%20bring%20change%20in%20the%20world%2C%20one%20lake%20at%20a%20time.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Padmashree%20Pande%2C%20Images%20Courtesy%3A%20Dayanand%20Krishnan%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721995199000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-23-at-20.28.41-min-1721993798.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D358580%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20residents%20of%20Chitlapakkam%20in%20Chennai%20have%20restored%20a%2050-acre%20lake%20after%20years%20of%20efforts%2C%20petitions%2C%20cleaning%20drives%2C%20and%20a%20relentless%20campaign%20called%20%23SavingChitlapakkamLake.%20Their%20efforts%20resulted%20in%20the%20state%20sanctioning%20Rs%2025%20crores%20for%20the%20project.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Paris%20Olympics%20Opening%20Ceremony%3A%20Performers%2C%20Timing%20And%20All%20Other%20Details%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Opening%20Ceremony%20of%20Paris%20Olympics%202024%20is%20set%20to%20be%20the%20one%20of%20its%20kind%20with%20the%20event%20set%20to%20take%20place%20at%20the%20Seine%20River%20in%20the%20French%20capital.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20ever%2C%20the%20opening%20ceremony%20will%20be%20held%20outside%20a%20stadium%2C%20instead%20the%20city%20of%20Paris%20will%20be%20turned%20into%20a%20grand%20arena.%20A%20whopping%2010%2C500%20athletes%20are%20set%20to%20sail%20across%20the%20Seine%2C%20and%20the%20two%20representatives%20for%20India%20are%20veteran%20table%20tennis%20star%20Achanta%20Sharath%20Kamal%20and%20shuttler%20PV%20Sindhu.%20The%20Opening%20Ceremony%20is%20expected%20to%20start%20at%2011%20PM%20IST%20(7%3A30%20PM%20local%20time).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%26quot%3BFirst%20of%20its%20kind%26quot%3B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20far%20as%20the%20Opening%20Ceremony%20is%20concerned%2C%20it%20won't%20take%20place%20inside%20a%20stadium%20this%20time.%20The%20Seine%20River%20in%20Paris%20will%20witness%20almost%20100%20boats%20carrying%20an%20estimated%2010%2C500%20athletes%20will%20float%20along%20the%20Seine%20during%20the%20parade.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMajority%20of%20the%20206%20National%20Olympic%20Committees%20(NOCs)%20represented%20in%20the%20parade%20will%20have%20boats%20to%20themselves%2C%20while%20the%20smaller%20ones%20will%20share%20boats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20boats%20will%20be%20equipped%20with%20cameras%20to%20allow%20television%20and%20online%20viewers%20to%20see%20the%20athletes%20up%20close.%20The%20boat%20parade%20will%20conclude%20after%20covering%20a%206-kilometre%20route%20at%20the%20Trocadero.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Olympics'%20official%20website%2C%20the%20opening%20ceremony%20is%20open%20to%20as%20many%20people%20as%20possible%20is%20a%20first.%20Eighty%20giant%20screens%20and%20strategically%20placed%20speakers%20will%20allow%20everyone%20to%20enjoy%20the%20magical%20atmosphere%20of%20this%20show%20reverberating%20throughout%20the%20French%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Opening%20Ceremony%20for%20the%20Olympic%20Games%20Paris%202024%20will%20be%20the%20largest%20in%20Games%20history.%20It%20will%20be%20open%20to%20all%3A%20residents%20from%20Paris%20and%20its%20region%2C%20as%20well%20as%20visitors%20from%20all%20over%20France%20and%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EParade%20route%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20parade%20will%20commence%20at%20the%20Austerlitz%20bridge%20(East)%20beside%20the%20Jardin%20des%20Plantes%20and%20will%20conclude%20at%20the%20Trocadero%20(West).%20The%20opening%20ceremony%20make%20its%20way%20around%20the%20two%20islands%20at%20the%20centre%20of%20the%20city%20(the%20Ile%20Saint%20Louis%20and%20the%20Ile%20de%20la%20Cite)%20before%20passing%20under%20several%20bridges%20and%20gateways.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAthletes%20on%20board%20the%20parade%20boats%20will%20get%20glimpses%20of%20some%20of%20the%20official%20Games%20venues%2C%20including%20Parc%20Urbain%20La%20Concorde%2C%20the%20Esplanade%20des%20Invalides%2C%20the%20Grand%20Palais%2C%20and%20lastly%20the%20Iena%20bridge%20where%20the%20parade%20will%20come%20to%20a%20stop%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPerformers%20and%20star%20attractions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20per%20multiple%20reports%2C%20singers%20Celine%20Dion%20and%20Lady%20Gaga%20are%20most%20likely%20to%20perform.%20French-Malian%20R%26amp%3BB%20star%20Aya%20Nakamura%20is%20also%20rumoured%20to%20be%20part%20of%20the%20star-studded%20line-up.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1721994480000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-07%2F8d9j08r_paris-olympics-2024_625x300_25_July_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Folympics-2024%2Fparis-olympics-2024-opening-ceremony-performers-timing-venue-and-all-other-details-6186247%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20th