-for-smaller-innovative-tech-companies%2Farticleshow%2F112040317.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-boosts-financing-support-for-smaller-innovative-tech-companies%2Famp_articleshow%2F112040317.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fchina%2Fchina-boosts-financing-support-for-smaller-innovative-tech-companies%2Famp_articleshow%2F112040317.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Plant%201%20Tree%20In%20Your%20Life%E2%80%99%3A%207%20Heroes%20Protecting%20India%E2%80%99s%20Coastline%20With%20Lakhs%20of%20Mangrove%20Trees%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Worldwide%2C%20a%20fifth%20of%20them%20%5Bmangroves%5D%20have%20already%20disappeared%E2%80%99%20reads%20a%20July%202023%20coverage%20by%20the%20UNEP%20(United%20Nations%20Environment%20Programme).%20The%20pace%20with%20which%20these%20salt-tolerant%20wetland%20species%20are%20being%20wiped%20off%20is%20unsettling.%20One%20would%20almost%20begin%20to%20assume%20their%20role%20is%20negligible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20that%E2%80%99s%20where%20the%20mangroves%20themselves%20urge%20us%20to%20rethink.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UNEP%20report%20is%20a%20comprehensive%20glance%20at%20the%20critical%20role%20that%20these%20tropical%20trees%20play%20in%20ensuring%20the%20planet%E2%80%99s%20wheels%20function%20well.%20Being%20%E2%80%9Cone%20of%20the%20only%20trees%20that%20thrive%20in%20salty%20waters%E2%80%9D%2C%20mangroves%20act%20as%20%E2%80%9Cnurseries%E2%80%9D%20for%20over%201%2C500%20plant%20and%20animal%20species%20that%20live%20in%20the%20coastal%20belts.%20As%20if%20that%20wasn%E2%80%99t%20impressive%2C%20they%20make%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F260147%2Finitiative-saving-mumbai-mangorves-environment-godrej-and-boyce%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeffective%20car