%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20mother%20informed%20me%20that%20her%20child%20cannot%20sit%20still%20in%20one%20place%20for%20more%20than%20three%20minutes.%20She%20was%20very%20afraid%20of%20the%20idea%20of%20taking%20him%20to%20learn%20weaving%2C%20a%20skill%20that%20requires%20focus%20and%20attention.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBut%20after%20the%20first%20five%20minutes%2C%20the%20child%20found%20the%20work%20engaging%20and%20continued%20to%20weave%20for%20half%20an%20hour%20without%20getting%20distracted.%20His%20mother%20became%20so%20overwhelmed%20to%20see%20this%20that%20she%20broke%20down.%20The%20kid%20had%20anger%20or%20temperamental%20issues%20but%20weaving%20provided%20him%20calmness.%20This%20gave%20me%20an%20idea%20to%20introduce%20DIY%20kits%20as%20occupational%20therapy%20for%20children%20with%20disabilities%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20initiative%20has%20already%20gained%20traction%20with%2010%20schools%20showing%20interest%20in%20including%20weaving%20as%20part%20of%20their%20curriculum%2C%20alongside%20partnerships%20for%20homeschooling%2C%20workshops%2C%20and%20textile%20exhibitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Kalaiyarasi%2C%20this%20venture%20is%20not%20just%20a%20business%20but%20a%20heartfelt%20mission%20to%20contribute%20to%20society.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20only%20doing%20the%20business%20but%20we%20are%20doing%20something%20for%20the%20community.%20Hearing%20stories%20of%20such%20children%20and%20mothers%20is%20very%20rewarding%20for%20me.%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20this%20initiative%20is%20demonstrating%20how%20traditional%20skills%20can%20be%20adapted%20for%20modern%20times%20to%20foster%20creativity%20and%20wellbeing%20of%20the%20community%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EFor%20more%20details%2C%20you%20can%20check%20the%20looms%20at%20Raatai%20Handloom%E2%80%99%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.raatai.com%2Fcategory%2F455296%2Fhandloom%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3Eofficial