ates%20submitting%20their%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20to%20potential%20employers%20and%20becoming%20a%20beacon%20of%20hope%20in%20an%20otherwise%20challenging%20job%20market.%20Some%20celebrated%20promising%20job%20offers%2C%20while%20others%20prepared%20for%20successive%20rounds%20of%20interviews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTwo%20people%20with%20dwarfism%20got%20employed%20with%20Amazon%20through%20the%20fair.%20Since%20they%20were%20working%20from%20places%20where%20Amazon%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20offices%2C%20they%20were%20given%20WFH%20opportunities.%20A%20laptop%2C%20a%20table%2C%20and%20every%20other%20work%20equipment%20that%20they%20might%20need%20were%20also%20provided%20by%20the%20company%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBecause%20the%20word%20of%20the%20job%20fair%20had%20spread%20around%2C%20organisations%20which%20previously%20were%20not%20big%20on%20hiring%20candidates%20with%20disabilities%20had%20shown%20up%20as%20well.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThe%20long-term%20impact%20of%20equal%20opportunities%20on%20the%20community%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDisha%20says%20that%20to%20her%20knowledge%2C%20there%20are%20two%20more%20organisations%20that%20work%20for%20people%20with%20dwarfism%20in%20southern%20India%2C%20but%20are%20only%20restricted%20to%20a%20few%20states.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGiven%20that%20The%20Little%20People%20of%20India%20is%20the%20only%20pan-India%20organisation%20working%20for%20the%20community%2C%20and%20that%20Disha%20is%20an%20internationally-acclaimed%20para%20athlete%2C%20her%20organisation%20came%20into%20the%20limelight%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201080px)%20100vw%2C%201080px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-07-22-at-17.37.36-2-1721660254.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22At%