e%20entire%20farm.%20The%20cow%20dung%20and%20urine%20are%20converted%20into%20natural%20fertilisers%2C%20such%20as%20%3Cem%3Epanchagavya%2C%20jeevamruth%2C%20amirtha%20karaisal%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%20and%20vermicompost.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20the%20answers%20we%20are%20looking%20for%20are%20present%20in%20traditional%20farming.%20I%20wanted%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20efforts%20of%20my%20forefathers%20and%20father%20in%20building%20this%20farm%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20go%20to%20waste.%20Farmers%20have%20been%20practising%20soil%20conservation%20and%20balancing%20the%20ecosystem%20for%20ages.%20I%20use%20their%20knowledge%20with%20a%20small%20twist%20of%20technology%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Saravanan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESince%20making%20the%20fertilisers%20manually%20is%20a%20time-consuming%20process%2C%20he%20installed%20a%20biodigester%2C%20which%20produces%20seven%20times%20the%20output%20that%20was%20being%20produced%20earlier.%20All%20the%20waste%20generated%20in%20the%20cow%20shed%20is%20sent%20to%20the%20fermentation%20chamber%2C%20generating%20almost%207%2C000%20litres%20of%20fertilisers%20daily%2C%20as%20per%20the%20farmer.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC5IhIfZSWFr%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC5IhIfZSWFr%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%